page.title: 20Compilers of Felton Survey
page.content:
The report was compiled by members of the Felton and Preston Wynne Womens' Institute, together with a few non-members. The Institute has 28 members, 8 of whom helped with this report.
Mrs.S.Bowen, materials controller,J.P. Mrs.J.Edwards, farmer's wife,J.P. Mrs.H.Ford, sub-postmistresss Mrs.P.Ford, farmer's wife Mrs.J.Gaydon, head teacher Miss S.Gaydon, student Mrs.H.Jones, music teacher Mrs.M.Roby, geology teacher Mr.B.Roby, educational adviser Mrs.V.Spencer, general factotum Miss G.Watkins, W.I.treasurer Mrs.D.Westoby, farmer's wife
The report was filed on disc by Dr.A.Murgatroyd, college tutor
